lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur striker Harry Kane believes the club are challenging for their first title for 55 years because there are "no bad eggs" in one of the hardest-working squads in the Premier League.

headline.print_headline: Team Spirit the Key to Spurs' Title Challenge Says Kane
